| What | Where |
|------|-------|
| All generation controls | `frontend/src/views/StudioView.tsx` |
| Slider helper component | `StudioView.tsx:12-24` — `SF` component |
| Spinner helper component | `StudioView.tsx:26-38` — `Spin` component |
