uv run uvicorn backend.server:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8600 --reload
```

```bash
# Terminal 2 — frontend
cd frontend && npm run dev
```

The frontend's `vite.config.ts` proxies `/api/*` to `http://localhost:8600`, so same-origin fetches Just Work.

